OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny mist or low cloud soon
OL,6,Fburning off. It will remain dry with
OL,7,Fvariable amounts of cloud and some
OL,8,Fbright or sunny spells, the best of
OL,9,Fthese in the afternoon. Becoming very
OL,10,Fwarm to hot with some cooling sea
OL,11,Fbreezes.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA warm sunny evening then a
OL,14,Fdry and mainly clear night, though low
OL,15,Fcloud and mist on north coast may
OL,16,Fdrift down the Bann Valley.
OL,17,
OL,18,CFriday:FLow cloud and mist near north
OL,19,Fcoast burning off then a dry bright
OL,20,Fday with variable cloud and some sunny
OL,21,Fspells. Very warm to hot.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
