OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA dry
OL,6,Fweekend with bright or sunny spells
OL,7,Fbut the mornings starting cloudy.
OL,8,FMonday dry and sunny. Very warm.
